snippet.title: Pico Playtime: Boomby
snippet.description: In this video I play through Boomby by Picoter8, a platformer made for LOWREZJAM 2020. Boomby is a rhythm platformer where you are a bomb who can jump by exploding and explore a level with keys and coins to find and multiple paths to victory.
